package: NotesOverlay
author: Tony Lyons
version: 1.1
rv: 3.0
requires: ''

modes:
  - file: NotesOverlay
    load: immediate

mu:
  - file: notes_dialog
    load: immediate

description: |
  Review notes overlay plugin for OpenRV.
  Adds Review > Add Note menu (Shift+N) for adding text annotations to frames.

  Features:
  - Multi-line text input with copy/paste support
  - White text with black outline for readability on any background
  - Smart text wrapping
  - Notes stack vertically on the same frame
  - Timeline markers on frames with notes
  - Notes persist in RVPaint node properties (survives session save/autosave)
